 “奥本海默”仍在中国做着巨大的生意https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-still-doing-huge-business-in-china-3503940?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oppenheimer-is-still-doing-huge-business-在中国Hollie GeraghtyMon, 25 Sep 2023 21:04:31 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3503940 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>克里斯托弗·诺兰的历史史诗在中国 IMAX 取得巨大成功</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-still-doing-huge-business-in-china-3503940">《奥本海默》在中国仍然做着巨大生意的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>上周末， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>在中国的票房数字接近 6000 万美元（4900 万英镑）。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片像一颗炸弹一样击中大脑</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/china-box-office-oppenheimer-holding-strong-60m-1235597893/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《好莱坞报道》</a></em>数据报道，从上周五（9 月 22 日）到周日（24 日），克里斯托弗·诺兰的这部历史史诗增加了 250 万美元（200 万英镑）的绘画费用，使总金额接近 5810 万美元（4750 万英镑）。来自票房追踪器 Artisan Gateway。</p><p>该片排名第四，仅次于中国新犯罪惊悚片<em>《尘埃落定》、《敢死队》</em>和中国大片<em>《赌注》</em> 。</p><p>自近一个月前上映以来， <em>《奥本海默》</em>在中国 IMAX 上取得了巨大成功，本周末票房收入为 74 万美元（60.6 万英镑），总票房为 1,700 万美元（1,390 万英镑）。这也是2023年在中国上映的第四大美国电影。 </p><figure id="attachment_3476542" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3476542" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3476542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Cillian-Murphy-Oppenheimer-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3476542" class="wp-caption-text"> 《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲。图片来源：环球影业</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-passes-bohemian-rhapsody-most-successful-biopic-ever-3499601">这部由希里安·墨菲主演的剧情片也成为本月有史以来票房最高的传记片</a>，超过了之前的纪录保持者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bohemian-rhapsody-film-reviews-queen-movie-2393540">《波西米亚狂想曲》</a> 。</p><p>该片目前全球票房收入超过 9.127 亿美元（7.36 亿英镑），超过了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">女王</a>传记片的 9.108 亿美元（7.345 亿英镑），成为票房最成功的传记片。</p><p> <em>《奥本海默》</em>已经打破了多项票房记录，最近成为有史以来最成功的第二次世界大战相关电影。这也是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-surpasses-marvel-blockbuster-to-set-new-box-office-milestone-3494494">2023 年票房第三高的电影，</a>仅次于<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/super-mario-bros-movie-review-chris-pratt-3425797"><em>《超级马里奥兄弟大电影》</em></a> 。</p><p>希里安<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy)</a>饰演 J. 罗伯特·奥本海默 ( <em>Oppenheimer</em> )，他是“原子弹之父”，在原子弹的制造过程中发挥了至关重要的作用。影片中艾米莉·布朗特饰演基蒂·奥本海默，马特·达蒙饰演莱斯利·格罗夫斯将军，小罗伯特·唐尼饰演刘易斯·施特劳斯，弗洛伦斯·皮尤饰演吉恩·塔特洛克。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对该片的<i>五星级</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">评论</a>中表示：“<em>奥本海默</em>不仅是对原子弹背后的人的权威描述，也是成人电影制作领域的一项里程碑式的成就。</p><p>本月早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/you-can-read-full-oppenheimer-script-free-3496639"><em>奥本海默</em>的剧本在网上免费发布</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oppenheimer-is-still-doing-huge-business-in-china-3503940">《奥本海默》在中国仍然做着巨大生意的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
